Belirlenen K ile K-Means Modelinin Kurulması¶

In [ ]:
kmean = KMeans(n_clusters=3,random_state=42).fit(Pca)
kmean_data = pd.DataFrame(Pca,columns=["Çekirdek Boyutu","Asimetrisi"])
In [ ]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10,10),dpi=100);
sns.scatterplot(x=Pca.transpose()[0], y=Pca.transpose()[1],hue=kmean.labels_,palette =sns.color_palette("dark:salmon_r", as_cmap=True));
plt.scatter(kmean.cluster_centers_[:,0], kmean.cluster_centers_[:,1], marker="*", c="red", s=250, label="centroids");

plt.ylabel("Asimetrisi")

In [ ]:
for i in ["K-Mean Labels","Agro Labels"]:
    if "K-Mean" in i:
        sls = silhouette_score(kmean_data[["Çekirdek Boyutu","Asimetrisi"]],kmean_data["K-Mean Labels"])
        cs = completeness_score(kmean_data["True Label"],kmean_data["K-Mean Labels"])
        hcv = homogeneity_completeness_v_measure(kmean_data["True Label"],kmean_data["K-Mean Labels"])
        print(f'K-Means Skorları\nSilhouette : {sls}\nCompleteness : {cs}\nHomogeneity : {hcv[0]}\nV_Ölçüsü : {hcv[1]}')
    else:
        sls = silhouette_score(kmean_data[["Çekirdek Boyutu","Asimetrisi"]],kmean_data["Agro Labels"])
        cs = completeness_score(kmean_data["True Label"],kmean_data["Agro Labels"])
        hcv = homogeneity_completeness_v_measure(kmean_data["True Label"],kmean_data["Agro Labels"])
        print(f'Agro Skorları\nSilhouette : {sls}\nCompleteness : {cs}\nHomogeneity : {hcv[0]}\nV_Ölçüsü : {hcv[1]}')

Random Forest Modeli Kurulumu¶

GridSearchCV ile En İyi Parametrelerin Bulunması¶

In [ ]:
param_grid = {"n_estimators":np.arange(50,501,50),
"max_features":["sqrt"],
"criterion":["gini", "entropy"],
"ccp_alpha":[0.01,0.05,.1],
"max_samples":np.arange(3,X_train.shape[1],1)}
GSC = GridSearchCV(RandomForestClassifier(random_state=13),param_grid=param_grid,cv=10,verbose=0,n_jobs=1,scoring="accuracy")
GSC.fit(X_train,y_train)
GSC.best_params_
In [ ]:
gridRes =pd.DataFrame(GSC.cv_results_)
gridRes = gridRes[["param_ccp_alpha","param_criterion","param_max_features","param_max_samples","param_n_estimators","mean_test_score"]]
gridRes = gridRes.sort_values(by="mean_test_score",ascending=False)
gridRes = gridRes[gridRes["param_criterion"] == "gini"]
In [ ]:
sns.lineplot(x=gridRes["param_n_estimators"],y=gridRes["mean_test_score"]*100,hue="param_max_samples",data=gridRes,palette=sns.color_palette("hls", 4));
plt.xlabel("Ormandaki Ağaç Sayısı");
plt.ylabel("Eğitim Verisi Doğruluk oranı (%)")
plt.legend(title="Maks Örneklem Sayısı");

GridSearchCV İle En İyi Parametrelerin Bulunması¶

In [ ]:
param_grid = {"eta":np.arange(0,.5,0.1),
"min_child_weight":np.arange(1,5,1),
"max_depth":np.arange(3,8,1),
"n_estimators":np.arange(50,351,50)}
GSCXB = GridSearchCV(XGBClassifier(eval_metric="auc",use_label_encoder=False,booster="gbtree"),param_grid=param_grid,cv=10,verbose=1,scoring="accuracy")
GSCXB.fit(X_train,y_train)

              importance_type=None, interaction_constraints='',
